<p>“Put any more thought into the idea of a donor?”</p>
<p>Slinking lower into the passenger seat, Erin gave a half-hearted shrug. “Not really any more than before. Just want someone we know already and who we trust. Don’t want to go to a bank.”</p>
<p>Aaron nodded and settled back into his seat as they made their way onto the highway. “Anyone you can think of, minkypie?”</p>
