<p><em><span>7:33 PM Markus</span></em></p>
<p>So the more I thought about what I had planned, the less I really wanted to go through with it. So I tried to just sit there and talk with your parents about you and all the good time and stuff.</p>
<p><em><span>7:33 PM Markus</span></em></p>
<p>I tried earnestly to patch things up, but your mom just told me she remembered things differently.</p>
<p><em><span>7:34 PM Markus</span></em></p>
